## Summary
This documentation explains how to create and manage behavioral cohorts in Amplitude, which are user groups defined by specific actions performed within a time period, including creation through the Cohorts tab or Microscope feature, importing from CSV files, and comparing cohorts using segmentation modules and interval cohorts.

